  "commit_message": "Bump org.elasticsearch:elasticsearch from 7.13.4 to 8.19.8 in /ms/neng\n\nBumps org.elasticsearch:elasticsearch from 7.13.4 to 8.19.8.\n## Release notes\n\nSourced from org.elasticsearch:elasticsearch's releases.\n\nElasticsearch 8.19.8\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.19/release-notes-8.19.8.html\nElasticsearch 8.19.7\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.19/release-notes-8.19.7.html\nElasticsearch 8.19.6\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.19/release-notes-8.19.6.html\nElasticsearch 8.19.5\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.19/release-notes-8.19.5.html\nElasticsearch 8.19.4\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.19/release-notes-8.19.4.html\nElasticsearch 8.19.3\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.19/release-notes-8.19.3.html\nElasticsearch 8.19.2\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.19/release-notes-8.19.2.html\nElasticsearch 8.19.1\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.19/release-notes-8.19.1.html\nElasticsearch 8.19.0\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.19/release-notes-8.19.0.html\nElasticsearch 8.18.8\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.18/release-notes-8.18.8.html\nElasticsearch 8.18.7\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.18/release-notes-8.18.7.html\nElasticsearch 8.18.6\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\nRelease notes: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/8.18/release-notes-8.18.6.html\nElasticsearch 8.18.5\nDownloads: https://elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\n\n... (truncated)\n\n## Commits\n\ne34ace0 Add validation to DER parser for seq len (#138683) (#138697)\n219189f Update Gradle wrapper to 9.2.1 (#138482) (#138693)\n8be0982 Add user profile size limit (#138691)\na8ec260 [8.19] Add length validation for rename_replacement parameter in snapshot res\nf2dae0f Extend timeout in IngestGeoIpClientYamlTestSuiteIT (#138610) (#138646)\nb564aa8 [ES-13486] Skipping ES builds on non supported jdk versions (#138262) (#138629)\n0f3f4e9 [8.19] fix(semantic highlighter): add vector similarity queries and bbq_disk\nbf5d48a Upgrading commons-lang3 version for repository-hdfs plugin (#138589) (#138613)\n51a0709 ILM Explain: valid JSON on truncated step info (#137638) (#138606)\n394ea7d Adjust two today()/current_date() tests to create less noise (#138588) (#138598)\nAdditional commits viewable in compare view\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nSigned-off-by: dependabot[bot] <support@github.com>\nChange-Id: I1020d37e94d7a77cb194c72a129a3cb1fe5289cc\nGitHub-PR: https://github.com/onap/ccsdk-apps/pull/7\nGitHub-Hash: cd605ba5bdeac9da\nSigned-off-by: onap.gh2gerrit <releng+onap-gh2gerrit@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
